{"type":"message","id":"6af7dc6d","parentId":"926cbd89","timestamp":"2026-05-09T14:23:15.386Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_upunsgnwu7p3_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/home/apinan/.hermes/node/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/ci.md:- **Fast path** runs for pull requests touching Docker/package surfaces, bundled plugin package/manifest changes, or core plugin/channel/gateway/Plugin SDK surfaces that the Docker smoke jobs exercise. Source-only bundled plugin changes, test-only edits, and docs-only edits do not reserve Docker workers. The fast path builds the root Dockerfile image once, checks the CLI, runs the agents delete shared-workspace CLI smoke, runs the container gateway-network e2e, verifies a bundled extension build arg, and runs the bounded bundled-plugin Docker profile under a 240-second aggregate command timeout (each scenario's Docker run capped separately).\n/home/apinan/.hermes/node/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/help/debugging.md:`--reset` wipes config, credentials, sessions, and the dev workspace (using\n/home/apinan/.hermes/node/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/help/faq.md:    Native installs land in the active workspace `skills/` directory. For shared skills across agents, place them in `~/.openclaw/skills/<name>/SKILL.md`. If only some agents should see a shared install, configure `agents.defaults.skills` or `agents.list[].skills`. Some skills expect binaries installed via Homebrew; on Linux that means Linuxbrew (see the Homebrew Linux FAQ entry above). See [Skills](/tools/skills), [Skills config](/tools/skills-config), and [ClawHub](/tools/clawhub).\n/home/apinan/.hermes/node/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/help/faq.md:    - **Local by default:** sessions, memory files, config, and workspace live on the Gateway host\n/home/apinan/.hermes/node/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/help/faq.md:    Your **workspace** (AGENTS.md, memory files, skills, etc.) is separate and configured via `agents.defaults.workspace` (default: `~/.openclaw/workspace`).\n/home/apinan/.hermes/node/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/help/faq.md:    Default workspace is `~/.openclaw/workspace`, configurable via:\n/home/apinan/.hermes/node/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/help/faq.md:    Relative paths resolve inside the workspace, but absolute paths can access other\n/home/apinan/.hermes/node/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/help/faq.md:    - Dev reset: `openclaw gateway --dev --reset` (dev-only; wipes dev config + credentials + sessions + workspace).\n/home/apinan/.hermes/node/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/help/faq.md:    - `tools.fs.workspaceOnly=true` keeps local-path sends limited to workspace, temp/media-store, and sandbox-validated files.\n/home/apinan/.hermes/node/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/help/testing-updates-plugins.md:  without losing config, agents, sessions, workspaces, plugin allowlists, or"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":16,"aggregated":"/home/apinan/.hermes/node/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/ci.md:- **Fast path** runs for pull requests touching Docker/package surfaces, bundled plugin package/manifest changes, or core plugin/channel/gateway/Plugin SDK surfaces that the Docker smoke jobs exercise. Source-only bundled plugin changes, test-only edits, and docs-only edits do not reserve Docker workers. The fast path builds the root Dockerfile image once, checks the CLI, runs the agents delete shared-workspace CLI smoke, runs the container gateway-network e2e, verifies a bundled extension build arg, and runs the bounded bundled-plugin Docker profile under a 240-second aggregate command timeout (each scenario's Docker run capped separately).\n/home/apinan/.hermes/node/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/help/debugging.md:`--reset` wipes config, credentials, sessions, and the dev workspace (using\n/home/apinan/.hermes/node/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/help/faq.md:    Native installs land in the active workspace `skills/` directory. For shared skills across agents, place them in `~/.openclaw/skills/<name>/SKILL.md`. If only some agents should see a shared install, configure `agents.defaults.skills` or `agents.list[].skills`. Some skills expect binaries installed via Homebrew; on Linux that means Linuxbrew (see the Homebrew Linux FAQ entry above). See [Skills](/tools/skills), [Skills config](/tools/skills-config), and [ClawHub](/tools/clawhub).\n/home/apinan/.hermes/node/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/help/faq.md:    - **Local by default:** sessions, memory files, config, and workspace live on the Gateway host\n/home/apinan/.hermes/node/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/help/faq.md:    Your **workspace** (AGENTS.md, memory files, skills, etc.) is separate and configured via `agents.defaults.workspace` (default: `~/.openclaw/workspace`).\n/home/apinan/.hermes/node/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/help/faq.md:    Default workspace is `~/.openclaw/workspace`, configurable via:\n/home/apinan/.hermes/node/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/help/faq.md:    Relative paths resolve inside the workspace, but absolute paths can access other\n/home/apinan/.hermes/node/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/help/faq.md:    - Dev reset: `openclaw gateway --dev --reset` (dev-only; wipes dev config + credentials + sessions + workspace).\n/home/apinan/.hermes/node/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/help/faq.md:    - `tools.fs.workspaceOnly=true` keeps local-path sends limited to workspace, temp/media-store, and sandbox-validated files.\n/home/apinan/.hermes/node/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/help/testing-updates-plugins.md:  without losing config, agents, sessions, workspaces, plugin allowlists, or","cwd":"/home/apinan/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778336595386}}
{"type":"message","id":"ed7a2a80","parentId":"6af7dc6d","timestamp":"2026-05-09T14:23:19.916Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found it! The correct config path is `agents.defaults.workspace`, not `workspace.path`. Let me try that.\n","thinkingSignature":"415a679f8d87d3ac3ac4cffcc55b8ba6128b2ed7849cc8f5c9cddf6f9951562d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_js7kzp1ypm50_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw config set agents.defaults.workspace \"/mnt/c/Users/Apinan/Dropbox/owen-workspace\" 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":692,"output":79,"cacheRead":33792,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34563,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778336595388,"responseId":"064e76547b10176156dab51174ad27ab"}}
{"type":"message","id":"1b7cf134","parentId":"ed7a2a80","timestamp":"2026-05-09T14:23:23.659Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_js7kzp1ypm50_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Config overwrite: /home/apinan/.openclaw/openclaw.json (sha256 97e9ae78c82486bdb7b6c640f83351f2d661138e71748bff62e1a7d70872d610 -> a55b07483f6eb5ecb2e9e7cccf610bf83daf725408683395de48b35dd07d509e, backup=/home/apinan/.openclaw/openclaw.json.bak)\nUpdated agents.defaults.workspace. Restart the gateway to apply."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":3732,"aggregated":"Config overwrite: /home/apinan/.openclaw/openclaw.json (sha256 97e9ae78c82486bdb7b6c640f83351f2d661138e71748bff62e1a7d70872d610 -> a55b07483f6eb5ecb2e9e7cccf610bf83daf725408683395de48b35dd07d509e, backup=/home/apinan/.openclaw/openclaw.json.bak)\nUpdated agents.defaults.workspace. Restart the gateway to apply.","cwd":"/home/apinan/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778336603658}}
{"type":"message","id":"842ec02e","parentId":"1b7cf134","timestamp":"2026-05-09T14:23:31.833Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The config was set successfully. Now the workspace path is set to the Dropbox folder. I need to restart the gateway for it to take effect. Let me do that.\n","thinkingSignature":"9275f2cd9aa85bdf7e6a7b7ef8058cebce14d2ec3b438312676ccbfe98bab0f7"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nเปลี่ยนเรียบร้อยแล้วครับ 🧑🏼‍💻 ตอนนี้ workspace ชี้ไปที่ Dropbox แล้ว\n\nRestart gateway ก่อนเพื่อให้มัน apply:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_p249h7ac56b7_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw gateway restart 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":238,"output":139,"cacheRead":34432,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34809,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778336603660,"responseId":"064e765c40db6b4a1461803ad49cab1d"}}
