{"type":"message","id":"946981c7","parentId":"701174b1","timestamp":"2026-05-09T15:04:37.512Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying \"กูพูดประสาดให้\" which means \"I'm speaking clearly for you\" or \"I speak clearly for you.\" This is a bit of a sarcastic/frustrated response to something - probably because the transcription before was wrong or unclear, and now they're saying they ARE speaking clearly. Maybe they're testing the transcription again or frustrated that I couldn't understand.\n","thinkingSignature":"1af497de5c323d29570923c3a51c25733beff5952ec24002299e49b480df9fd3"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**ผล transcription:**\n\n> กูพูดประสาดให้\n\n(แปลว่า \"กูพูดชัดให้แล้ว\" นะ — กำลังบอกว่าพูดชัดๆ แล้วไง 😄)\n\nเข้าใจแล้วครับเจ้านาย ไม่ต้องพูดซ้ำ 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":178,"output":211,"cacheRead":48960,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49349,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778339069182,"responseId":"064e7fff358b47afef00bb2d99e3cc3d"}}
