{"type":"message","id":"82e0578b","parentId":"30fbbe5f","timestamp":"2026-05-09T15:05:01.232Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is clarifying that they spoke in Thai, and the transcription should reflect Thai language. Looking back at the third audio, the transcription was \"กูพูดประสาดให้\" - this actually might be a mistranscription. The user is saying they were speaking Thai, so maybe the phrase was different. \"ประสาด\" isn't a real Thai word - it could be \"ชัด\" misheard as \"สาด\". The user is probably correcting me and saying \"กูพูดชัดให้\" (I spoke clearly for you) but the model misheard.\n\nWait - the sender is robberzaz (the boss), and they sent \"กูพูดประสาดให้\" - that doesn't make sense as Thai. It could be \"กูพูดประสาอะไร\" or maybe it's \"กูพูดให้ชัด\" or something. But the user just said \"กูพูดภาษาไทย\" - so they're confirming it was Thai.\n\nActually I think they might be saying \"กูพูดประสบสาดให้\" or something else - maybe they said something about speaking and the model misheard. \n\nActually, thinking about this more - the user might just be confirming the transcription. Looking at what was captured - \"กูพูดประสาดให้\" doesn't translate to anything coherent in Thai. What could they have said?\n\n\"กูพูดประสาอะไร\" (what are you talking about?)\n\"กูพูดให้ชัด\" (I speak so it's clear)\n\n\n\"กูพูดสาดให้\" (not real)\n\"กูพูดประสาด\" (not real)\n\nActually I wonder if the user said something like \"กูพูดให้ดู\" or \"กูพูดให้เข้าใจ\" - but it got mis-transcribed. Or maybe \"กูพูดประสาด\" could be a regional dialect or accent that got misread. The user just said they were speaking Thai so I should acknowledge that the transcription came through as Thai, even if the specific words don't make complete sense.","thinkingSignature":"2e374abcc2e86a12fc79c387e6115e823c46e6584e095b360762c83496d02a5c"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nรู้แล้วครับ 🧑🏼‍💻 ตอบกลับถูกต้อง — ภาษาไทย \"กูพูดประสาดให้\" หรืออาจจะเป็น \"กูพูดให้ชัด\" ที่ Whisper ฟังผิดไปนิดหน่อย 😄\n\nเจ้านายพูดอะไรมาครับ? 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":694,"output":661,"cacheRead":48416,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49771,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778339082966,"responseId":"064e800d74e02462eea48393380da8bd"}}
