{"type":"message","id":"08902ae1","parentId":"8647c984","timestamp":"2026-05-09T15:15:01.199Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Got transcription for file_14:\n\"ตอบมาเป็นเสียงด้วยได้ไหม\" = \"Can you reply with voice too?\"\n\nThe user is asking if I can reply with voice! They want me to speak back to them rather than text.\n\nLet me respond to this question. The user is asking if I can respond with voice. I can - I have TTS capabilities or I could generate an audio response. Let me think about what the user is asking.\n\nThey seem to be asking \"Can you reply with voice too?\" - basically asking if I can send voice messages back instead of just text.\n\nI should let the user know that I can - maybe using TTS. Let me check if there's a TTS setup.\n","thinkingSignature":"083826eb8b6d3d06cce07e5b83031b3dadee47b16ece4842ade6c5a7c5ec8e6d"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**ผล transcription:**\n\n> ตอบมาเป็นเสียงด้วยได้ไหม\n\nเจ้านายถามว่าผมตอบกลับเป็นเสียงได้ไหมใช่ไหมครับ 🧑🏼‍💻\n\n**ตอบได้ครับ** — มี TTS อยู่ ถ้าเจ้านายอยากให้ผมส่ง voice message ตอบกลับบ้าง\n\nแต่ต้องใช้ model เสียงที่รองรับภาษาไทยด้วย จะให้ผมตั้งค่า TTS ให้ reply เป็นเสียงเลยไหมครับ? 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":235,"output":408,"cacheRead":51552,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52195,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778339693170,"responseId":"064e826f703cc1a16ed342be72c4879c"}}
