{"type":"message","id":"597bf848","parentId":"28c4006d","timestamp":"2026-05-09T15:52:35.597Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good transcription:\n\"ตั้งได้รึยังที่ให้ตอบเป็นภาษาไทย\"\n\nThis means: \"Have you set it up yet so that it replies in Thai?\"\n\nThe user is asking if I've set up the Thai TTS yet. Let me answer honestly - I set messages.tts.auto to \"off\" and the Microsoft TTS was sending English. I haven't successfully set up Thai TTS yet. The user wants Thai voice replies.","thinkingSignature":"1cd511477e89882ec3fe3a772e239251b65da87b32d761ef9d048f13cc9eb2f0"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**ผล:**\n\n> ตั้งได้รึยังที่ให้ตอบเป็นภาษาไทย\n\n**ยังไม่ได้ตั้งครับเจ้านาย!** 🧑🏼‍💻 ตอนนี้ TTS ยังปิดอยู่ เพราะตั้งไว้มันส่ง English\n\nผมต้องดู doc เพิ่มว่า Microsoft TTS ตั้ง language/thai voice ได้ยังไง — จะทำให้เลยครับ 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":142,"output":292,"cacheRead":66080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66514,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778341942193,"responseId":"064e8b38a08123975a3330f56b8cfc4f"}}
