{"type":"message","id":"d72a6910","parentId":"bded3d67","timestamp":"2026-05-09T15:58:56.528Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_f4x54wj5sk0o_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"size=       0kB time=00:00:00.00 bitrate=N/A speed=N/A    \r[out#0/wav @ 0x5d8e13d44c80] video:0kB audio:117kB subtitle:0kB other streams:0kB global headers:0kB muxing overhead: 0.064939%\nsize=     117kB time=00:00:03.75 bitrate= 256.2kbits/s speed=74.7x"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":221,"aggregated":"size=       0kB time=00:00:00.00 bitrate=N/A speed=N/A    \r[out#0/wav @ 0x5d8e13d44c80] video:0kB audio:117kB subtitle:0kB other streams:0kB global headers:0kB muxing overhead: 0.064939%\nsize=     117kB time=00:00:03.75 bitrate= 256.2kbits/s speed=74.7x","cwd":"/mnt/c/Users/Apinan/Dropbox/owen-workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778342336527}}
{"type":"message","id":"8eb76b57","parentId":"d72a6910","timestamp":"2026-05-09T15:58:56.529Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_f4x54wj5sk0o_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"and deliver native voice messages on Feishu, Matrix, Telegram, and WhatsApp,\naudio attachments everywhere else, and PCM/Ulaw streams for telephony and Talk.\n\n## Quick start\n\n<Steps>\n--\n    OpenAI and ElevenLabs are the most reliable hosted options. Microsoft and\n    Local CLI work without an API key. See the [provider matrix](#supported-providers)\n    for the full list.\n  </Step>\n  <Step title=\"Set the API key\">\n    Export the env var for your provider (for example `OPENAI_API_KEY`,\n    `ELEVENLABS_API_KEY`). Microsoft and Local CLI need no key.\n  </Step>\n  <Step title=\"Enable in config\">\n    Set `messages.tts.auto: \"always\"` and `messages.tts.provider`:\n\n    ```json5\n--\n| **Azure Speech**  | `AZURE_SPEECH_KEY` + `AZURE_SPEECH_REGION` (also `AZURE_SPEECH_API_KEY`, `SPEECH_KEY`, `SPEECH_REGION`)          | Native Ogg/Opus voice-note output and telephony.                        |\n| **DeepInfra**     | `DEEPINFRA_API_KEY`                                                                                              | OpenAI-compatible TTS. Defaults to `hexgrad/Kokoro-82M`.                |\n| **ElevenLabs**    | `ELEVENLABS_API_KEY` or `XI_API_KEY`                                                                             | Voice cloning, multilingual, deterministic via `seed`.                  |\n| **Google Gemini** | `GEMINI_API_KEY` or `GOOGLE_API_KEY`                                                                             | Gemini API TTS; persona-aware via `promptTemplate: \"audio-profile-v1\"`. |\n| **Gradium**       | `GRADIUM_API_KEY`                                                                                                | Voice-note and telephony output.                                        |\n| **Inworld**       | `INWORLD_API_KEY`                                                                                                | Streaming TTS API. Native Opus voice-note and PCM telephony.            |\n| **Local CLI**     | none                                                                                                             | Runs a configured local TTS command.                                    |\n| **Microsoft**     | none                                                                                                             | Public Edge neural TTS via `node-edge-tts`. Best-effort, no SLA.        |\n| **MiniMax**       | `MINIMAX_API_KEY` (or Token Plan: `MINIMAX_OAUTH_TOKEN`, `MINIMAX_CODE_PLAN_KEY`, `MINIMAX_CODING_API_KEY`)      | T2A v2 API. Defaults to `speech-2.8-hd`.                                |\n| **OpenAI**        | `OPENAI_API_KEY`                                                                                                 | Also used for auto-summary; supports persona `instructions`.            |\n| **OpenRouter**    | `OPENROUTER_API_KEY` (can reuse `models.providers.openrouter.apiKey`)                                            | Default model `hexgrad/kokoro-82m`.                                     |\n| **Volcengine**    | `VOLCENGINE_TTS_API_KEY` or `BYTEPLUS_SEED_SPEECH_API_KEY` (legacy AppID/token: `VOLCENGINE_TTS_APPID`/`_TOKEN`) | BytePlus Seed Speech HTTP API.                                          |\n| **Vydra**         | `VYDRA_API_KEY`                                                                                                  | Shared image, video, and speech provider.                               |\n| **xAI**           | `XAI_API_KEY`                                                                                                    | xAI batch TTS. Native Opus voice-note is **not** supported.             |\n| **Xiaomi MiMo**   | `XIAOMI_API_KEY`                                                                                                 | MiMo TTS through Xiaomi chat completions.                               |\n\nIf multiple providers are configured, the selected one is used first and the\nothers are fallback options. Auto-summary uses `summaryModel` (or\n`agents.defaults.model.primary`), so that provider must also be authenticated\n--"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":46,"aggregated":"and deliver native voice messages on Feishu, Matrix, Telegram, and WhatsApp,\naudio attachments everywhere else, and PCM/Ulaw streams for telephony and Talk.\n\n## Quick start\n\n<Steps>\n--\n    OpenAI and ElevenLabs are the most reliable hosted options. Microsoft and\n    Local CLI work without an API key. See the [provider matrix](#supported-providers)\n    for the full list.\n  </Step>\n  <Step title=\"Set the API key\">\n    Export the env var for your provider (for example `OPENAI_API_KEY`,\n    `ELEVENLABS_API_KEY`). Microsoft and Local CLI need no key.\n  </Step>\n  <Step title=\"Enable in config\">\n    Set `messages.tts.auto: \"always\"` and `messages.tts.provider`:\n\n    ```json5\n--\n| **Azure Speech**  | `AZURE_SPEECH_KEY` + `AZURE_SPEECH_REGION` (also `AZURE_SPEECH_API_KEY`, `SPEECH_KEY`, `SPEECH_REGION`)          | Native Ogg/Opus voice-note output and telephony.                        |\n| **DeepInfra**     | `DEEPINFRA_API_KEY`                                                                                              | OpenAI-compatible TTS. Defaults to `hexgrad/Kokoro-82M`.                |\n| **ElevenLabs**    | `ELEVENLABS_API_KEY` or `XI_API_KEY`                                                                             | Voice cloning, multilingual, deterministic via `seed`.                  |\n| **Google Gemini** | `GEMINI_API_KEY` or `GOOGLE_API_KEY`                                                                             | Gemini API TTS; persona-aware via `promptTemplate: \"audio-profile-v1\"`. |\n| **Gradium**       | `GRADIUM_API_KEY`                                                                                                | Voice-note and telephony output.                                        |\n| **Inworld**       | `INWORLD_API_KEY`                                                                                                | Streaming TTS API. Native Opus voice-note and PCM telephony.            |\n| **Local CLI**     | none                                                                                                             | Runs a configured local TTS command.                                    |\n| **Microsoft**     | none                                                                                                             | Public Edge neural TTS via `node-edge-tts`. Best-effort, no SLA.        |\n| **MiniMax**       | `MINIMAX_API_KEY` (or Token Plan: `MINIMAX_OAUTH_TOKEN`, `MINIMAX_CODE_PLAN_KEY`, `MINIMAX_CODING_API_KEY`)      | T2A v2 API. Defaults to `speech-2.8-hd`.                                |\n| **OpenAI**        | `OPENAI_API_KEY`                                                                                                 | Also used for auto-summary; supports persona `instructions`.            |\n| **OpenRouter**    | `OPENROUTER_API_KEY` (can reuse `models.providers.openrouter.apiKey`)                                            | Default model `hexgrad/kokoro-82m`.                                     |\n| **Volcengine**    | `VOLCENGINE_TTS_API_KEY` or `BYTEPLUS_SEED_SPEECH_API_KEY` (legacy AppID/token: `VOLCENGINE_TTS_APPID`/`_TOKEN`) | BytePlus Seed Speech HTTP API.                                          |\n| **Vydra**         | `VYDRA_API_KEY`                                                                                                  | Shared image, video, and speech provider.                               |\n| **xAI**           | `XAI_API_KEY`                                                                                                    | xAI batch TTS. Native Opus voice-note is **not** supported.             |\n| **Xiaomi MiMo**   | `XIAOMI_API_KEY`                                                                                                 | MiMo TTS through Xiaomi chat completions.                               |\n\nIf multiple providers are configured, the selected one is used first and the\nothers are fallback options. Auto-summary uses `summaryModel` (or\n`agents.defaults.model.primary`), so that provider must also be authenticated\n--","cwd":"/mnt/c/Users/Apinan/Dropbox/owen-workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778342336528}}
{"type":"message","id":"35edda39","parentId":"8eb76b57","timestamp":"2026-05-09T15:59:00.400Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me now run the transcription while also looking at the TTS config options for setting Thai language.","thinkingSignature":"314affcd2aeb011d176909f6b0a4afe4eefec35ead3c92775c67ae999a629d74"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1mh7ghwakale_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"/home/apinan/.hermes/hermes-agent/venv/bin/python3 - <<'EOF'\nfrom faster_whisper import WhisperModel\n\nmodel = WhisperModel(\"large-v3\", device=\"cpu\", compute_type=\"int8\")\nsegments, info = model.transcribe(\"/tmp/audio_msg21.wav\", beam_size=5)\nprint(f\"Detected language: {info.language}\")\nfor segment in segments:\n    print(segment.text)\nEOF\n","timeout":90}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3164,"output":147,"cacheRead":65248,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68559,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778342336533,"responseId":"064e8cc1eaf50c5a0097c6f3dd213363"}}
