{"type":"message","id":"ddc67ffc","parentId":"85d43227","timestamp":"2026-05-09T15:59:14.614Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_rqcj3p580c8j_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"normalized to `microsoft` and `openclaw doctor --fix` rewrites persisted\nconfig; new configs should always use `microsoft`.\n</Warning>\n\n## Configuration\n\nTTS config lives under `messages.tts` in `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`. Pick a\npreset and adapt the provider block:\n\n<Tabs>\n  <Tab title=\"Azure Speech\">\n```json5\n{\n  messages: {\n    tts: {\n      auto: \"always\",\n      provider: \"azure-speech\",\n      providers: {\n        \"azure-speech\": {\n          apiKey: \"${AZURE_SPEECH_KEY}\",\n          region: \"eastus\",\n          voice: \"en-US-JennyNeural\",\n--\n          // Optional natural-language style prompts:\n          // audioProfile: \"Speak in a calm, podcast-host tone.\",\n          // speakerName: \"Alex\",\n        },\n      },\n    },\n  },\n}\n```\n  </Tab>\n  <Tab title=\"Gradium\">\n```json5\n{\n  messages: {\n    tts: {\n      auto: \"always\",\n      provider: \"gradium\",\n      providers: {\n        gradium: {\n          apiKey: \"${GRADIUM_API_KEY}\",\n          voiceId: \"YTpq7expH9539ERJ\",\n--\n      provider: \"microsoft\",\n      providers: {\n        microsoft: {\n          enabled: true,\n          voice: \"en-US-MichelleNeural\",\n          lang: \"en-US\",\n          outputFormat: \"audio-24khz-48kbitrate-mono-mp3\",\n          rate: \"+0%\",\n          pitch: \"+0%\",\n        },\n      },\n    },\n  },\n}\n```"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":68,"aggregated":"normalized to `microsoft` and `openclaw doctor --fix` rewrites persisted\nconfig; new configs should always use `microsoft`.\n</Warning>\n\n## Configuration\n\nTTS config lives under `messages.tts` in `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`. Pick a\npreset and adapt the provider block:\n\n<Tabs>\n  <Tab title=\"Azure Speech\">\n```json5\n{\n  messages: {\n    tts: {\n      auto: \"always\",\n      provider: \"azure-speech\",\n      providers: {\n        \"azure-speech\": {\n          apiKey: \"${AZURE_SPEECH_KEY}\",\n          region: \"eastus\",\n          voice: \"en-US-JennyNeural\",\n--\n          // Optional natural-language style prompts:\n          // audioProfile: \"Speak in a calm, podcast-host tone.\",\n          // speakerName: \"Alex\",\n        },\n      },\n    },\n  },\n}\n```\n  </Tab>\n  <Tab title=\"Gradium\">\n```json5\n{\n  messages: {\n    tts: {\n      auto: \"always\",\n      provider: \"gradium\",\n      providers: {\n        gradium: {\n          apiKey: \"${GRADIUM_API_KEY}\",\n          voiceId: \"YTpq7expH9539ERJ\",\n--\n      provider: \"microsoft\",\n      providers: {\n        microsoft: {\n          enabled: true,\n          voice: \"en-US-MichelleNeural\",\n          lang: \"en-US\",\n          outputFormat: \"audio-24khz-48kbitrate-mono-mp3\",\n          rate: \"+0%\",\n          pitch: \"+0%\",\n        },\n      },\n    },\n  },\n}\n```","cwd":"/mnt/c/Users/Apinan/Dropbox/owen-workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778342354614}}
{"type":"message","id":"6c2b41eb","parentId":"ddc67ffc","timestamp":"2026-05-09T15:59:23.379Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see the Microsoft TTS config. I need to change the voice and lang to Thai. Let me find the Thai voice name for Microsoft TTS.\n\nLooking at the config example:\n```json5\n{\n  messages: {\n    tts: {\n      auto: \"always\",\n      provider: \"microsoft\",\n      providers: {\n        microsoft: {\n          enabled: true,\n          voice: \"en-US-MichelleNeural\",\n          lang: \"en-US\",\n          outputFormat: \"audio-24khz-48kbitrate-mono-mp3\",\n          rate: \"+0%\",\n          pitch: \"+0%\",\n        },\n      },\n    },\n  },\n}\n```\n\nI need to change `lang` to `th-TH` and `voice` to a Thai male voice. \n\nI'm looking through Microsoft's Thai voice catalog to find a suitable male neural voice that would work for the configuration.\n","thinkingSignature":"f2573760bc1eb3fda4b7623bbffe2f3184d9d8dda62038af5f588dfc87042f57"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ejb918x0oonz_1","name":"process","arguments":{"action":"poll","sessionId":"keen-bison","timeout":60000}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":430,"output":235,"cacheRead":68576,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69241,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778342354621,"responseId":"064e8cd36e2e4ed307175526f12894dd"}}
