{"type":"message","id":"e726d4dc","parentId":"c3289018","timestamp":"2026-05-09T16:04:54.610Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The transcription says: \"ลองส่งเสียงเป็นประสาธายมาหน่อย\" which means \"Try sending a test voice message\" - the boss is asking me to send a test voice message to see if the Thai TTS works.\n\nBut wait - I need to restart the gateway first for the TTS changes to take effect. Let me restart and then try to send a TTS message.\n\nActually, let me check if the gateway was restarted already or not. Earlier it was aborted with SIGTERM which means it was killed but might not have restarted. Let me restart it and then test TTS.","thinkingSignature":"40195693538b9c967927646863082bfb63c5d59598693dc12237d76c3a27a208"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n**ผล:**\n\n> ลองส่งเสียงเป็นประสาธายมาหน่อย\n\nเจ้านายอยากให้ลองส่งเสียงทดสอบ TTS ไทยใช่ไหมครับ!\n\nเดี๋ยว restart gateway ก่อนให้โหลด config ใหม่ แล้วส่งเสียงทดสอบเลยครับ 🧑🏼‍💻\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gupbsywiiz5r_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw gateway restart 2>&1","yieldMs":5000}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":130,"output":330,"cacheRead":72096,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72556,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778342685638,"responseId":"064e8e20c86f134d8694bf03efe087d3"}}
