{"type":"message","id":"9bdce764","parentId":"62e7468d","timestamp":"2026-05-09T16:07:24.808Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying \"วู้ยังไม่เห็นมึงส่งมาให้เลย เมื่อไรมึงจะส่งเป็นเสียงมาสักที\" - basically \"still haven't seen you send it, when will you send voice\"\n\nBut I did send! Maybe the Telegram message didn't deliver the voice, or the TTS setting isn't working properly. Let me check the TTS status and try to test if the auto TTS is actually sending.\n","thinkingSignature":"d1375d3b7d4d27cc5f7b88e0075d80958c9ae5dc3471fb2f720b45a21cc2c5a4"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n**ผล:**\n\n> วู้ยังไม่เห็นมึงส่งมาให้เลย เมื่อไรมึงจะส่งเป็นเสียงมาสักที\n\nเจ้านายบอกว่ายังไม่ได้รับเสียงที่ผมส่งเลย — งั้น TTS auto อาจจะยังไม่ทำงาน 🧑🏼‍💻\n\nเดี๋ยวเช็ค�ถานะ TTS ก่อนครับ:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_w2r4aduavfvs_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw config get messages.tts 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":170,"output":339,"cacheRead":73440,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73949,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778342837036,"responseId":"064e8eb70d6900575e628ea6317637c1"}}
