{"type":"message","id":"6fc37ff6","parentId":"6c88d7a4","timestamp":"2026-05-09T16:11:21.360Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is frustrated asking when I'll send voice. They're still not hearing any voice messages from me. TTS should be working since auto is set to \"always\". But maybe the TTS isn't generating properly. Let me check if there's a problem with the TTS setup.\n\nActually, the user's message includes \"To send an image back, prefer the message tool...\" which suggests there might be something wrong with how OpenClaw is sending the TTS response. Maybe the Microsoft provider isn't generating the audio properly.\n\nLet me try to send a test TTS using the /tts command to see if it works.","thinkingSignature":"506722153ab8cfb0f2482f542594a130ca61f33c7fe42b3584ea2d454a8fe154"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n**ผล:**\n\n> ผมบอกว่าให้ส่งมาเป็นเสียงเมื่อไรมึงจะส่งมาสับที\n\nเจ้านายยังไม่ได้ยินเสียงเลยใช่ไหมครับ? ขอโทษครับ — TTS อาจจะยังส่งไม่ได้\n\nลองใช้คำสั่ง `/tts status` ดูได้ไหมครับ? หรือบอกผมว่า Telegram ที่เจ้านายใช้อยู่ เป็น account ไหนครับ? (account ID `default` ใช่ไหม?) 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":149,"output":357,"cacheRead":75488,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75994,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778343073308,"responseId":"064e8fa21e6775b1b28271c9903f0b99"}}
